### ========================================
### CREATE USER (POST /api/users)
### ========================================

### 1. Caso de Éxito: Crear usuario válido
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lucia",
  "email": "lucia@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123"
}

### 2. Caso de Fallo: Usuario duplicado (mismo username o email)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lucia",
  "email": "nuevo@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123"
}

### 3. Caso de Fallo: Contraseñas no coinciden (Error del middleware)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "juan",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password321"
}

### 4. Caso de Fallo: Error de validación de Mongoose (username muy corto)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "a",
  "email": "corto@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123"
}

### ========================================
### GET USER (GET /api/users/:name)
### ========================================

### 5. Caso de Éxito: Obtener usuario existente
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/lucia

### 6. Caso de Fallo: Obtener usuario que no existe (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/usuario_fantasma

### ========================================
### UPDATE USER (PATCH /api/users/:name)
### ========================================

### 7. Caso de Éxito: Actualizar usuario
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/lucia
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/mi_nuevo_avatar.png",
  "email": "lucia_nuevo_correo@example.com"
}

### 8. Caso de Fallo: Actualizar sin campos válidos (400 Bad Request)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/lucia
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hola": "mundo"
}

### 9. Caso de Fallo: Actualizar usuario que no existe (404)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/usuario_fantasma
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "fantasma@example.com"
}

### ========================================
### DELETE USER (DELETE /api/users/:name)
### ========================================

### 10. Caso de Éxito: Eliminar usuario existente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/lucia

### 11. Caso de Fallo: Eliminar usuario que no existe (404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/lucia
